title: Why Full Stack Development is so important
contents: Full Stack Development allows the developer to view system development at a high level. This allows proped design decisions to be made.

title: Technologies for MVC apps.
contents: The following apps/technologies are needed at a minimum: HTML, JavaScript, and relational databases.

title: Why a full-stack developer needs a good breakfast
contents: The human brain needs protein! A breakfast high in protein is essential for a developers productivity.
